{"tid":1850813,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴，你究竟賣撚夠廣告未","createTime":"2020-01-29T17:19:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T11:06:56.000Z","uid":207077,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fb18d5ab7156dfcb26a65ce4678bf0e7319c4b2b","tid":1850813,"uid":207077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:19:50.000Z","msg":"屌你老母次撚次趕時間開九巴Apps睇既時候<br />\n你就係度賣撚埋d濕鳩一拳超人廣告<br />\n好啦以家想睇定聽日搭車個車程時間<br />\n個廣告直程整唔撚走<br />\n真係用撚燥<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gnWD9Pg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgnWD9Pg.png&h=27ced709&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa0237853eab45fc18761a6f00f3c275ceba2a2a","tid":1850813,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:20:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/308/5d9705d903228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F308%2F5d9705d903228.jpg&h=786cb045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港共正利用武漢肺炎進行第9步：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">種族清洗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n透過邊境不設防<br />\n高調宣揚非本地人士免費優先治療武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蓄意引導大量染病支那人來港<br />\n摧毀香港已經長期超負荷的醫療系統，令香港人大規模感染<br />\n而無法隔離或治理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n中共打算將香港將變成武漢，市民無法睇醫生，橫屍街頭<br />\n意圖對香港人進行大屠殺</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n香港人，仲唔反佢老母？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97596c773419dbd23f74c4f5a614e3d2ac00bd9d","tid":1850813,"uid":174058,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:26:37.000Z","msg":"開得呢d App都係好趕時間<br />\n仲要花時間熄廣告<br />\n次次都覺得恔<br />\n<br />\n不過九巴app點都比城巴新巴app好"},{"pid":"26a1a302f24c875ecc694f8abc3cbb157e42ab41","tid":1850813,"uid":168522,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:54:57.000Z","msg":"樓主應該慶幸自己唔洗搭新巴城巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67ceab477d9303f78c8cf9da88d20420057431d7","tid":1850813,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26a1a302f24c875ecc694f8abc3cbb157e42ab41","tid":1850813,"uid":168522,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:54:57.000Z","msg":"樓主應該慶幸自己唔洗搭新巴城巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T08:55:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac